title: Symbol search result POJO for SBF, SBS, and SBN requests. See Symbol Lookup via TCP/IP

Symbol.title: All characters uppercase. Can include Symbols such as (but not limited to) @+-=.# or spaces.

ListedMarketID.title: Numeric whole number referencing which market the symbol is listed on. Valid values can be acquired from the SLM command.

SecurityTypeID.title: Numeric whole number referencing which security type the symbol falls under. Valid values can be acquired from the SST command.

Description.title: The name of the company or a description of what the symbol represents.

SICCode.title: Numeric Whole number referencing which SIC code the symbol is listed under. Valid values can be acquired from the SSC command. Note: this value is only present for SBS request.

NIACCode.title: Numeric Whole number referencing which NIAC code the symbol is listed under. Valid values can be acquired from the SNC command. Note: this value is only present for SBN request.
